Rh and Au flat samples were used for normalization:
Cyclic activation. One cycle time 80 sec.
Reactor reactivity was measured with and without Cd
Ionization boron chmber KNT-52 in paraffin block
of 100 mm diameter. Filled witrh Ar.
Block-factors were used for extrapolation to zero
Of compiler. Min/max energies are not given in the
En-MIN = 0.5 eV was assumed by compiler.
Cr powder of weight 14.153 gram, 0.23 cm thickness.
Heavy water thermal column in PF-K reactor.

Cadmium ratio was measured by U-235 ionization chamber
to be 32.0 at the center of the thermal column.
Normalization was done by measurements on Rh,Au .
Resonance integral was determined from the measurement
results by usage of neutron statistical weight 0.67 for
